Package smarthome.domain.house.vo

Class Location

java.lang.Object
smarthome.domain.house.vo.Location
All Implemented Interfaces:
ValueObject
public class Location extends Object implements ValueObject
Represents a location in the smart home domain. A location is defined by an address and GPS coordinates. This class is a value object in the domain-driven design context.
